text: Newsroom is a online news website in New Zealand. It was founded by Tim Murphy and Mark Jennings in 2017 and is co-edited by them. It focuses on New Zealand politics, current affairs and social issues. It is using English. The website started on 2017 with the help of four "foundation sponsors", including the University of Auckland and Victoria University of Wellington. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:News websites Category:Websites established in the 2010s Category:2010s establishments in New Zealand Category:2017 establishments Category:Mass media in New Zealand
